reviews.review_text: WooHoo!! 2nd Show! My second show! I've been wainting a while for this download. This run was crazy (like most MSG shows of any band). The Farm Aid comments were really strange at the time, but great show all around. THANK YOU!!

Great Sounding AUD This is a pretty nice show. The Crazy Fingers, Uncle John's, Playin' is real sweet. Any show with a Box of Rain is a treat. I wish they would've played that tune a little more often. 
The sound is high quality grade A stuff. A perfect mix of crowd and music. I dig it. Hang loose.

good sound... ...good show.  1/2 step>all over now are good, and a high energy opener.  maggies farm rocks, though I think we all wished for the other one, per bob's direction, after the maggies rather than black peter. oh well. 3.5 for show, 4 for sound, rounded up.
whistling, talking, clapping Crowd too loud throughout the show.
